news_header: Lithuanian Foreign Minister Kestutis Budrys is visiting Finland to discuss bilateral relations and support for Ukraine.
news_text: Lithuanian Foreign Minister Kestutis Budrys is visiting Finland today. He will meet with Finnish Foreign Minister Elina Valtonen, President Alexander Stubb, and Defence Minister Antti Häkkänen. The discussions will focus on bilateral relations, the regional situation, support for Ukraine, and responses to hybrid threats. Mr. Budrys has been in office since December.
